---
layout: base.njk
title: Street Singers for Justice NYC
songs:
  - title: "Somebody's Hurting My Brother"
    author: "Yara Allen"
    verses:
      - ["Somebody's hurting my brother", "And it's gone on far too long", "Yes it's gone on far too long", "I tell you it's gone on far too long..."]
      - ["Somebody's hurting my brother", "And it's gone on far too long", "And we won't be silent any more!"]
      - ["Somebody's taking our Freedom..."]
  - title: "Singing For Our Lives"
    author: "Holly Near"
    verses:
      - ["We are a gentle angry people", "And we are singing, singing for our lives..."]
      - ["We won't let them take our neighbors..."]
  - title: "This Joy"
    author: "Resistance Revival Chorus"
    verses:
      - ["This joy that I have", "The world didn't give it to me", "The world didn't give it to me", "The world didn't give it to me..."]
      - ["The world didn't give it, the world can't take it away"]
      - ["This love that I have", "The world didn't give it to me..."]
  - title: "This Little Light of Mine"
    author: "Traditional spiritual, adapted for justice"
    verses:
      - ["This little light of mine", "I'm gonna let it shine", "I'm gonna let it shine", "I'm gonna let it shine..."]
      - ["Let it shine", "Let it shine", "Let it shine"]
      - ["Everywhere I go", "I'm gonna let it shine..."]
  - title: "We Get There Together"
    author: "Joshua Blaine"
    verses:
      - ["No one is getting left behind this time", "No one is getting left behind", "No one is getting left behind this time..."]
      - ["We get there together or we never get there at all", "We get there together or we never get there at all", "We get there together or we never get there at all..."]
  - title: "We Shall Not Be Moved"
    author: "Traditional spiritual, adapted for justice"
    verses:
      - ["We shall not, we shall not be moved", "We shall not, we shall not be moved..."]
      - ["Just like a tree that's planted by the water", "We shall not be moved..."]
      - ["We're fighting for justice..."]
  - title: "We Shall Overcome"
    author: "Traditional spiritual, adapted for civil rights"
    verses:
      - ["We shall overcome", "We shall overcome..."]
      - ["We shall overcome someday..."]
      - ["Oh, deep in my heart", "I do believe", "We shall overcome someday..."]
      - ["We are not afraid..."]
  - title: "Woke Up This Morning"
    author: "Traditional spiritual, adapted by Rev. Robert Osby"
    verses:
      - ["Woke up this morning with my mind", "Stayed on Freedom!"]
      - ["Woke up this morning with my mind", "Stayed on Freedom!"]
      - ["Woke up this morning with my mind", "Stayed on Freedom!"]
      - ["Hallelu, Hallelu, Hallelujah!"]
      - ["Marchin' and singin' with my mind..."]
---

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <a href="https://actionnetwork.org/forms/join-street-singers-for-justice-nyc/" target="_blank" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-md text-lg font-semibold shadow hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors mb-8 mt-8">Sign Up for Updates</a>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 mt-4">Street Singers for Justice NYC</h1>
    <div class="space-y-12 text-left">
        {% for song in songs %}
        <div class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 cursor-pointer hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors" onclick="toggleLyrics('song-{{ song.title | replace("'", "") | slug }}')">
                {{ song.title }}
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">(click to show/hide lyrics)</span>
            </h2>
            <div id="song-{{ song.title | replace("'", "") | slug }}" class="hidden">
                {% if song.author %}
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">by {{ song.author }}</p>
                {% endif %}
                {% for verse in song.verses %}
                <div class="mb-6">
                    {% for line in verse %}
                    <p class="mb-2">{{ line }}</p>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</div> 